.TH "snd_soc_runtime_calc_hw" 9 "snd_soc_runtime_calc_hw" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
snd_soc_runtime_calc_hw \- Calculate hw limits for a PCM stream
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" snd_soc_runtime_calc_hw
.BI "(struct snd_soc_pcm_runtime *rtd "  ","
.BI "struct snd_pcm_hardware *hw "  ","
.BI "int stream "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "rtd" 12
ASoC PCM runtime
.IP "hw" 12
PCM hardware parameters (output)
.IP "stream" 12
Direction of the PCM stream
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Calculates the subset of stream parameters supported by all DAIs
associated with the PCM stream.
